lead_paragraph: Paul O'Connell has been forced to retire from rugby due to injury before having the chance to end a glittering career with European champions Toulon, the former Ireland captain said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Ireland's O'Connell Hangs Up His Boots for Good
